0.1.name: wordpress/socibookcom-social-bookmarking-button
0.1.description: A Social Bookmarking button from SociBook. With the button you can add your Blog or Website content to the biggest Social Bookmarking sites (SociBook.com, Digg.com, Yahoo Buzz, Google, Delisious.com and Facebook). The button is a great way of getting traffic from the Social Bookmarking networks.
